  "3217360": {
    "name": "Reconquer Online",
    "steam_appid": 3217360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217360/extras/8675bba5265e876ec3a561780548664f.avif?t=1749653027\" width=598 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reconquer Online is an indie MMORPG that prioritizes <strong>fun</strong> and <strong>player freedom</strong> rather than grinding. This game introduces fresh mechanics like lever-controlled flame throwers, barricades, damaging fires, player collision, quests with alternative endings, lateral thinking puzzles, and different environmental interactions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are currently <strong>13 trainable skills, 11 quests, several bosses and challenges, and a competitive raid with high scores</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217360/extras/0b46100dad5b8a0405b5bb8f1c07df37.avif?t=1749653027\" width=596 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Reconquer online has many unique features. These include:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Player-controlled Resources:</strong> There is currently a player controlled mine and dock. Monsters sometimes drop &quot;essences&quot; which can be used to guard these resources. Whoever owns the resource has access to the items it generates. Other players can defeat the guardian monsters and claim the resource for themselves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Barricades and Fires:</strong> Barricades can be used to block others while fires can be used to injure them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mechanically unique bosses:</strong> Fight against bosses that spawn projectiles, drop boulders, switch attack styles, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless raids</strong> with high scores for those who have advanced the furthest.<br><strong>In-game macroing</strong> to automate the repetitive parts of game play.<br><strong>A caravan system</strong> instead of bank notes for transporting items.<br><strong>A Tiered PvP System:</strong> The PvP damage multiplier starts at 0% and slowly increases as you venture further. <br><strong>Public Enemies:</strong> PvP outside of the wasteland is punished with fidelity loss. Those with negative fidelity are designated &quot;public enemies&quot; and are vulnerable everywhere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Alternate Endings: </strong>Choose a side in certain quests and reap different rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217360/extras/e4588ef0d1390385470cbcd347d4bb1d.avif?t=1749653027\" width=598 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a game whose content will continue to grow with the player base.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We believe the game will end up better by slowly introducing higher level content rather than all at once. Our goal is to release a new tier of content (+5 levels) about every three months. In addition, there will be four new biomes. Each biome will have its own major quest-line, raid, and unique items.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desert (up to level 40 content)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jungle (Up to level 60)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arctic (Up to level 80)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wasteland (Up to level 99)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217360/extras/b956b0471519fb0d52a6d427e01e518b.avif?t=1749653027\" width=598 height=146 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The long term goal is to monetize solely through memberships. Membership currently gives you the ability to choose a custom name. In the future, membership will also give you access to content above level 20.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 months - $5</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 months - $10</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 Year - $15</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Membership can be purchased in game through Steam.</p>",
